, "end": 44.401, "text": "And then you train a big model, which is the teacher.", "words": [{"word": "And", "start": 39.493, "end": 39.573, "score": 0.882}, {"word": "then", "start": 39.633, "end": 39.793, "score": 0.713}, {"word": "you", "start": 39.853, "end": 40.074, "score": 0.695}, {"word": "train", "start": 40.134, "end": 40.494, "score": 0.835}, {"word": "a", "start": 40.514, "end": 40.534, "score": 0.999}, {"word": "big", "start": 40.574, "end": 41.756, "score": 0.867}, {"word": "model,", "start": 41.836, "end": 42.117, "score": 0.992}, {"word": "which", "start": 42.658, "end": 42.818, "score": 0.788}, {"word": "is", "start": 42.938, "end": 43.038, "score": 0.724}, {"word": "the", "start": 43.078, "end": 44.0, "score": 0.93}, {"word": "teacher.", "start": 44.04, "end": 44.401, "score": 0.923}]}, {"start": 45.703, "end": 54.777, "text": "And now what you want to do is you want to make you want to make that model maybe smaller, right, such that it runs on a mobile phone.", "words": [{"word": "And", "start": 45.703, "end": 45.863, "score": 0.764}, {"word": "now", "start": 45.903, "end": 46.544, "score": 0.91}, {"word": "what", "start": 46.804, "end": 46.945, "score": 0.794}, {"word": "you", "start": 46.965, "end": 47.065, "score": 0.766}, {"word": "want", "start": 47.105, "end": 47.245, "score": 0.751}, {"word": "to", "start": 47.285, "end": 47.345, "score": 0.993}, {"word": "do", "start": 47.385, "end": 47.505, "score": 0.998}, {"word": "is", "start": 47.586, "end": 47.666, "score": 0.871}, {"word": "you", "start": 47.766, "end": 47.866, "score": 0.815}, {"word": "want", "start": 47.906, "end": 48.086, "score": 0.784}, {"word": "to", "start": 48.146, "end": 48.247, "score": 0.968}, {"word": "make", "start": 48.327, "end": 48.547, "score": 0.898}, {"word": "you", "start": 49.168, "end": 49.248, "score": 0.998}, {"word": "want", "start": 49.288, "end": 49.429, "score": 0.833}, {"word": "to", "start": 49.689, "end": 49.789, "score": 0.994}, {"word": "make", "star